6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Beautiful.ai and Relume share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Ai Generation, Collaboration. Where Beautiful.ai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Brand Kit and Animations and Stock Assets, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Relume uniquely offers Responsive, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Beautiful.ai holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Relume scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Relume comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Beautiful.ai begins at $12/mo. Relume stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Beautiful.ai requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
