a:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Beautiful.ai is best suited for sales teams, consultants, business professionals, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Relume, meanwhile, shines for web designers, agencies, Webflow users, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2017, Beautiful.ai describes itself as \"AI presentation maker that automatically designs stunning slides.\" Relume, established in 2022, positions itself as \"AI website builder that generates sitemaps and wireframes from text prompts.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
b:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Beautiful.ai** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (8 vs 6). However, this does not mean Relume is a poor choice — far from it. Relume excels in its own right, particularly for web designers and agencies.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value ai auto-designs slides beautifully, go with Beautiful.ai. If ai sitemap and wireframe generation matters more to you, Relume is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
